Dialogue: 2,0:02:30.96,0:02:36.97,Mushisode Title,,0,0,0,eptitle,{\an6\fad(2000,0)\blur0.6\pos(1218,110)}Floral Delusion
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.15,0:02:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ever since I can remember,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.91,0:02:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}she's been living in our garden lodge.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.25,0:02:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.85,0:02:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}she lives there, as radiant and beautiful as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.37,0:03:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.39,0:03:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that reminds me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.17,0:03:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There's supposed to be a famous cherry tree around these parts.{lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.27,0:03:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps I'll stop by and take a look...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.73,0:03:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.00,0:03:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.01,0:03:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard there's a famous cherry tree around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.38,0:03:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know where it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.92,0:03:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that tree should be right down this path.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.13,0:03:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you from around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.27,0:03:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I come from the other side of the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.84,0:04:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I traveled here to get medicine for my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.80,0:04:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That so? Your mother must be very dear to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.09,0:04:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a renowned doctor living up ahead or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.31,0:04:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. He lives next to the cherry tree you asked about, and he's known for medicine that can cure any pain.{I know "cure"  here seems counter-intuitive, but it's a pretty common saying, especially for someone not in the doctor field.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.57,0:04:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.49,0:04:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.36,0:04:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, there's the tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.61,0:04:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.64,0:04:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not even blooming.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.05,0:04:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what's wrong with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.54,0:04:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.37,0:04:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll be taking my leave here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.12,0:04:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Good luck getting that medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.97,0:04:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to disturb you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.59,0:04:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.53,0:04:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.58,0:04:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard that you make medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.17,0:04:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother is ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.07,0:04:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.09,0:05:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you also ill?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.38,0:05:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.18,0:05:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Good health is the one thing I have going for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.59,0:05:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's very good to hear.{dun dun dunnnnn}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.69,0:05:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.22,0:05:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll prepare the medicine for your mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,so you should stay the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.46,0:05:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.03,0:05:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This tree is ancient.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.45,0:05:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It looks to be at least six or seven centuries old.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.89,0:05:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no sign of it having bloomed yet this season, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.29,0:05:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe it's withered from age and is no longer able to bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.17,0:05:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.41,0:05:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.79,0:05:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.76,0:05:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't even notice her.{length}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.17,0:05:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.97,0:06:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her beauty is so radiant that it gives me the chills.{how positively pulchritudinous}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.29,0:06:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But there's something odd about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.05,0:06:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.63,0:06:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.19,0:06:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Has this cherry tree not bloomed yet this year?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.13,0:06:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is she blind and deaf?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.13,0:06:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.99,0:06:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't seem to be from around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.51,0:06:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you want something with Saho?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.19,0:06:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really. It's just that something bothered me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.35,0:06:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you her husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.64,0:06:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I'm a relative, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.89,0:06:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me for asking,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.98,0:06:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,but has she lost her sight and hearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.79,0:06:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Almost entirely.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be because she's ingested the foam exuded by this tree?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.45,0:06:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Ginko, a mushi-shi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.75,0:07:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This tree is inhabited by the foam-like Kodama, or "Tree Spirit" mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.35,0:07:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Trees inhabited by Kodama generally live for a very long time
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.53,0:07:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and also bloom spectacularly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.57,0:07:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,However, when an animal ingests Kodama,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.90,0:07:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,it can lose one or more of its five senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.69,0:07:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be nice if we could ask her and find out whether that's the case here,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.08,0:07:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,but we cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.51,0:07:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, come with me, Saho.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.58,0:07:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You may get a chill if you're out here after dusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.77,0:07:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a doctor, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.01,0:07:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There's got to be some way you can look into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.85,0:07:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,My family has been but simple gardeners for generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.57,0:07:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Gardeners?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.86,0:07:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We are only capable of caring for plants and bringing out their beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.61,0:07:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This cherry tree here, for example, is {a strain that is }resilient against disease, but it bears very small flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.93,0:08:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,However, if you graft in branches from a tree{strain} that bears beautiful flowers,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the resilient cherry tree will come to bear beautiful flowers as well{ instead of small ones}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.31,0:08:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,While my family studied plants in this manner,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.17,0:08:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,we also began to create medicines from their flowers, \Nand share our results with others.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.65,0:08:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you made medicine from the mushi-infested cherry tree?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.81,0:08:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That tree is a special tree that my family has protected for generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.79,0:08:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We would never use it for such a purpose.{lol full o' shit.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.01,0:09:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this where you get your famous painkilling medicine?{Good ol' Ginko, not trusting anyone.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.35,0:09:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I already told you that it only deadens one's senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.41,0:09:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you're careful with how much you ingest,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.98,0:09:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,your senses will eventually return to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.19,0:09:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.08,0:09:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You experimented with her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.75,0:09:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.04,0:09:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I would never do such a horrible thing!{lol sure}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.49,0:09:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,My family has been researching plants for generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.19,0:09:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So of course when we discovered that strange foam{ coming out of that cherry tree},
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.62,0:09:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,we had to investigate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.49,0:09:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Three or so of my ancestors \Ncould see the strange foam.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.93,0:09:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Each of them studied it for years and devised a safe dosage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.27,0:09:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not the sap of a plant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.79,0:09:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The foam itself is alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.85,0:09:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything bad were to happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.91,0:09:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,would you be able to take countermeasures?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.55,0:09:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You must leave that behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.29,0:10:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But there are those who have need of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.55,0:10:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There are many who care not whether they can see or hear, so long as they can escape the suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.99,0:10:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What gives you the right to take that choice away from them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.63,0:10:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, first show me your family's research.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.81,0:10:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I will determine myself whether the findings are trustworthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.07,0:10:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. I'll show you to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.87,0:10:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,One more thing. About that woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.31,0:10:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If her condition is truly caused by the Kodama,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.28,0:10:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,we may be able to restore her sight and hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.05,0:10:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So, are you {\i1}sure{\i0} you don't know how she became that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.25,0:10:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a story that has been passed down since my great-grandfather was alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.17,0:10:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Your great-grandfather?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.59,0:10:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,A story from when he was a young man...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.03,0:11:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,A story from nearly eighty years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.37,0:11:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.85,0:11:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Who could have abandoned a baby like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.54,0:11:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.75,0:11:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this faint pink foam on her mouth?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.47,0:11:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it sap?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.18,0:11:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,She must have been so hungry \Nthat she sucked on the tree sap.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.71,0:11:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,My great-grandfather, Mansaku, took the infant home with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.35,0:11:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,However, his wife could not produce milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.75,0:12:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The infant even refused thin gruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.73,0:12:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing she would drink was the tree sap.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.59,0:12:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Mansaku's family cared for the child \Nas though she were one of their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.77,0:12:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But even after many years, the child hardly grew.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.61,0:12:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,She remained an infant for over a decade,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.02,0:12:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,still only willing to drink the sap of that cherry tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.93,0:12:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,After thirty years, Mansaku and his wife passed away,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.04,0:12:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,but Saho remained but a young girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.65,0:12:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come, Saho.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.69,0:12:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where's Mansaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.49,0:12:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Daddy Mansaku is no longer with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.25,0:12:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}From now on, you'll be living with me, your big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.97,0:12:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,By then,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.52,0:12:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Saho had almost completely lost use of all five senses, \Nincluding her sight and hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.81,0:13:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Moreover, she also fell ill periodically.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.79,0:13:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,During the years when Saho was in poor health,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.50,0:13:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,the giant cherry tree would not bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.05,0:13:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Subsequent generations continued to protect and cherish Saho.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.87,0:13:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Masaki, you must...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.24,0:13:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.85,0:13:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You must take care of Saho...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.91,0:13:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Saho...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.91,0:13:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.45,0:13:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,All of us have loved Saho as though she were the very spirit of that cherry tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.39,0:14:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Eighty years?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.13,0:14:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This means the Kodama bestows longevity and beauty to animals as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.29,0:14:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.46,0:14:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Can Saho be cured?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.67,0:14:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There is indeed a way to extract the Kodama.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.31,0:14:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.67,0:14:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,if we remove the Kodama from her and try to restore her senses,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.79,0:14:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Saho may not survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.94,0:14:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.75,0:14:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That is unfortunate, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.49,0:14:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,These are all of my family's records on the foam.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.34,0:14:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.85,0:14:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Saho?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.55,0:14:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't wait anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.19,0:15:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to do it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.85,0:15:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,May I have a word?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.33,0:15:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I've prepared the medicine,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.39,0:15:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'd like you to try it for yourself first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.60,0:15:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.97,0:15:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It is rare, but there are some who have poor reactions to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.55,0:15:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If you react well to it, your mother should be fine too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.07,0:15:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.99,0:15:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whoops.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.04,0:15:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Some of these are very old.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.38,0:15:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How many generations ago is this, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.05,0:15:50.05,mushibrushishi,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fax-0.3\c&H1B242C&\fscx82\fscy82\1a&HD0&\frz6.601\pos(973,308)\alpha&HD0&}Recorded by \N{\fs68}Mansaku
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.05,0:15:50.05,mushibrushishi,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8\fax-0.3\c&H1B242C&\fscx82\fscy82\1a&H8B&\frz6.601\pos(973,308)}Recorded by \N{\fs68}Mansaku
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.47,0:15:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He said Mansaku was his great-grandfather, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.65,0:15:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And yet, these look...
