Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.77,0:15:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There are four names scattered among the records.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.31,0:16:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Does that mean four successive generations were able to see mushi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.15,0:16:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That is extremely rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.07,0:16:08.07,mushibrushishi,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fax-0.3\c&H1B242C&\1a&HD0&\frz6.601\fscx113\fscy113\pos(591,182)\alpha&HD0&}Recorded by \N{\fs68}Mansaku
Dialogue: 1,0:16:05.07,0:16:08.07,mushibrushishi,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fax-0.3\c&H1B242C&\1a&HA6&\frz6.601\fscx113\fscy113\pos(591,182)}Recorded by \N{\fs68}Mansaku
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.05,0:16:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.80,0:16:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What I gave you just now was merely a sedative.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.49,0:16:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Due to interference, I couldn't give you the painkiller.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.57,0:16:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best to make this quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.05,0:16:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.34,0:16:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You will be able to keep on living.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.29,0:16:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You will be able to bloom once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.25,0:17:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.10,0:17:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's true?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.48,0:17:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been grafting whole bodies as you would tree branches—{length}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.10,0:17:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,all to keep her alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.91,0:17:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Not for a mere eighty years, either,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.61,0:17:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,but for centuries!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.23,0:17:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.91,0:17:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Mansaku was my ancestor from {\i1}eight{\i0} generations ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.63,0:17:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If we do not do this,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.48,0:17:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Saho's body will deteriorate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.23,0:17:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though she is still so beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.15,0:17:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.71,0:17:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,saku...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.33,0:17:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Saho?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.57,0:18:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.55,0:18:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.51,0:18:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Saho!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.87,0:18:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I won't let you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.55,0:18:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get you a new body right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.08,0:18:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.01,0:18:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Just how many lives have already been sacrificed for her to live?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.31,0:18:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.29,0:18:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps there {\i1}is{\i0} something wrong with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.69,0:18:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,For three hundred years, our family has loved a woman who is like a plant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.63,0:18:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.55,0:19:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you done?!{Oh my god!}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.79,0:19:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The fire! It's spreading to the tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.39,0:19:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.61,0:19:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cherry blossoms?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.33,0:19:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Saho, look at the cherry blossoms!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.31,0:20:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The tree has bloomed again—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.67,0:20:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Saho!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.68,0:20:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.41,0:20:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.19,0:20:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.12,0:20:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Saho!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.21,0:20:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It is said that some ancient trees come to possess souls of their own...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.57,0:20:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and thus entice and enthrall the hearts of men.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.03,0:20:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It is also said that should such a tree have a bloom that is beauteous and radiant,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.31,0:20:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the effect is even more profound.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.29,0:21:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The cherry tree avoided being burned to the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.31,0:21:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However, neither the gardener nor the woman were ever seen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.76,0:21:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, what beautiful cherry blossoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.03,0:21:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, they seem to melt away the weariness of travel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.54,0:21:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Care to take a rest around here, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.53,0:21:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a wonderful idea. \NA perfect place to enjoy a small drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.18,0:21:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in no hurry, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.91,0:21:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But my, what a splendid sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.22,0:22:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, there's nothing quite like it.
